para_trans: Senior Personal from the Selected Category Short Writer Post
Post-promotion to the post of Assistant
(Smt. A. A. Prabhu, Selected Short Writer)
Government Order No: ASC 1525 / P.No.30 / Pr. 3,
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Read: - The serial number of this section. 01.08.2025 Daily
The category selected from the selection list 2024-25 for the Ministry of Ministries is Short-List Subject to Reference.
Regular promotion to the post of Senior Personal Assistant has been given under the Government Order dated 01.08.2025.
The following select categories of short story writers in this order have been amended by making changes in their post-promotions:
The revised posting is being done in the section shown in column-6 in front of his name.
2.The said orders shall come into force with immediate effect.
The other terms and conditions contained in the relevant Government Order dated 01.08.2025 with respect to promotion shall continue.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
